## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023, and some sources may have more recent updates that are not included. Additionally, while the report focuses on human causes of climate change, it does not extensively cover natural factors that may also contribute to climate variability. The findings are based on the interpretation of available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the issue.